---
title: Creamy Tuscan-Inspired Salmon Stew with Savoury Leeks
description: Our juicy salmon is the star of the show here. Served in an ultra-velvety sun-dried tomato and cream sauce with savoury leeks and juicy tomatoes, this salmon needs nothing more than a finishing sprinkle of fresh parsley!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-tuscan-inspired-salmon-stew-b57160b9.jpg
